---shifts view

1) if user is employer, employer could view his/her own shifts both published and unpublished. This employer could not view the other employers offered shifts

2) if user is a nurse but not RN, then no RN shifts is visible. All employers published job vacancies could be reserved based on role permissions. RN, PN or Assistant

3) Admin and Staff could access all published shifts, update and remove it.


